{"Title":"蔓越莓牛轧糖的做法","Primary":["棉花糖155克","蔓越莓干200克","奶粉100克"],"Auxiliary":["黄油30克"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.将棉花糖切小块备用","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271641862997.jpg","2.蔓越莓干稍微切碎备用","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271642763093.jpg","3.黄油放入不粘锅中，小火加热","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271643798219.jpg","4.至完全融化","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271644866380.jpg","5.倒入棉花糖","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271645557122.jpg","6.不断搅拌","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271646338673.jpg","7.棉花糖和黄油会慢慢融合到一起，至完全融合后关火","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271647208672.jpg","8.加入奶粉","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271647952740.jpg","9.快速搅匀","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271648898040.jpg","10.加入蔓越莓干","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271649633076.jpg","11.搅匀","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271650633414.jpg","12.将糖团放到案板上稍微揉压几下","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271658498890.jpg","13.放入不沾烤盘中压平整","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271659451311.jpg","14.晾凉后切块即可","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271660265569.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271664488326.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/28/36/1009028/n1009028_142271664717611.jpg","烹饪技巧","1、棉花糖先切开，在加热时会更加容易与黄油融合到一起；2、蔓越莓干有些多了，一半的量应该就可以了。"]}